        </p>
        <div class="step-insight-pill">
          <span class="insight-dot"></span>
          "6 pertes sur 7 entre 15h–16h NY sur OB invalidés"
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Carrousel témoignages -->
    <div class="reviews-section reveal">
      <div class="reviews-header">
        <div class="reviews-stars-global">
          <span class="star">★</span><span class="star">★</span>
          <span class="star">★</span><span class="star">★</span>
          <span class="star">★</span>
          <span class="reviews-score">4.9/5</span>
        </div>
        <p class="reviews-count">Basé sur les retours de nos premiers utilisateurs</p>
      </div>

      <div class="reviews-carousel">
        <div class="reviews-track" id="reviewsTrack">

          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-top">
              <div class="review-avatar" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3b82f6,#22d3ee)">TM</div>
              <div class="review-meta">
                <div class="review-name">Thomas M.</div>
                <div class="review-profile">Day trader · Forex · Paris</div>
              </div>
              <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
            </div>
            <p class="review-text">
              "J'utilisais Tradervue avant. Le journal est similaire mais l'IA change tout.
