              vraiment solide."
            </p>
            <div class="review-footer">
              <span class="review-date">Utilisateur depuis 3 semaines</span>
              <span class="review-badge">Premium</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-top">
              <div class="review-avatar" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#10b981,#34d399)">AL</div>
              <div class="review-meta">
                <div class="review-name">Alexandre L.</div>
                <div class="review-profile">Prop firm trader · SMC · Bordeaux</div>
              </div>
              <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
            </div>
            <p class="review-text">
              "En prop firm tu dois être irréprochable sur la discipline.
              Le debrief hebdo de MTC m'a aidé à identifier mes schémas de revenge trading
              précisément. J'ai passé mon défi FTMO la semaine d'après.
              Je recommande à tous ceux qui font de la prop."
            </p>
            <div class="review-footer">
              <span class="review-date">Utilisateur depuis 2 mois</span>
              <span class="review-badge">Premium</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-top">
              <div class="review-avatar" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ef4444,#f97316)">MC</div>
              <div class="review-meta">
                <div class="review-name">Marie C.</div>
                <div class="review-profile">Day trader · Actions · Nantes</div>
              </div>
              <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
            </div>
            <p class="review-text">
              "J'ai importé 3 mois de trades d'un coup. L'IA a sorti une analyse
              que mon broker ne m'aurait jamais donnée — mes meilleures performances
              sont le mardi matin, mes pires le vendredi après-midi.
              J'ai adapté mes sessions et mon win rate a pris 8 points en 3 semaines."
            </p>
            <div class="review-footer">
              <span class="review-date">Utilisatrice depuis 5 semaines</span>
              <span class="review-badge">Premium</span>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <div class="reviews-controls">
          <button class="reviews-btn" id="reviewsPrev" aria-label="Précédent">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
              <path d="M15 18l-6-6 6-6"/>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="reviews-dots" id="reviewsDots">
            <button class="reviews-dot active" data-idx="0"></button>
            <button class="reviews-dot" data-idx="1"></button>
            <button class="reviews-dot" data-idx="2"></button>
            <button class="reviews-dot" data-idx="3"></button>
            <button class="reviews-dot" data-idx="4"></button>
          </div>
          <button class="reviews-btn" id="reviewsNext" aria-label="Suivant">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
              <path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/>
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="coach-cta reveal">
      <a href="https://app.mytradingcoach.app/register" class="btn-p">
        Créer mon profil trader gratuitement
        <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
          <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <p class="coach-cta-note">Aucune CB requise · 7 jours Premium offerts</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<script>
  const track = document.getElementById('reviewsTrack') as HTMLElement;
  const dots  = document.querySelectorAll<HTMLButtonElement>('.reviews-dot');
  const prev  = document.getElementById('reviewsPrev');
  const next  = document.getElementById('reviewsNext');
  if (!track) { throw new Error('reviewsTrack not found'); }

  let current = 0;
  const total = 5;

  function getVisible(): number {
    if (window.innerWidth < 768) return 1;
    if (window.innerWidth < 1024) return 2;
    return 3;
  }
  function maxIndex(): number { return total - getVisible(); }

  function goTo(idx: number) {
    current = Math.max(0, Math.min(idx, maxIndex()));
    const card = track.querySelector<HTMLElement>('.review-card');
    if (!card) return;
    const cardW = card.offsetWidth + 16;
    track.style.transform = `translateX(-${current * cardW}px)`;
    dots.forEach((d, i) => d.classList.toggle('active', i === current));
  }

  prev?.addEventListener('click', () => goTo(current - 1));
  next?.addEventListener('click', () => goTo(current + 1));
  dots.forEach((d, i) => d.addEventListener('click', () => goTo(i)));

  let timer = setInterval(() => goTo(current + 1 <= maxIndex() ? current + 1 : 0), 5000);
  track.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => clearInterval(timer));
  track.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {
    timer = setInterval(() => goTo(current + 1 <= maxIndex() ? current + 1 : 0), 5000);
  });
  window.addEventListener('resize', () => goTo(Math.min(current, maxIndex())));
</script>

<style>
  .coach-section {
    padding: 100px 5%;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .coach-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(59,130,246,.06) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .coach-wrap { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; }

  /* Comparaison */
  .coach-compare {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 72px;
  }

  .coach-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }

  .coach-col-label {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--txt2);
    font-family: var(--mono); letter-spacing: .3px;
  }

  .coach-col-ic {
    width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .bad-ic  { background: rgba(239,68,68,.15); color: #ef4444; }
  .good-ic { background: rgba(16,185,129,.15); color: #10b981; }

  .coach-bubble {
    border-radius: 14px; padding: 18px;
    display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .bad-bubble  { background: rgba(239,68,68,.05); border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.15); }
  .good-bubble { background: rgba(16,185,129,.05); border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,.2); }

  .coach-avatar {
    width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 18px; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .bad-av  { background: rgba(239,68,68,.1); }
  .good-av { background: rgba(16,185,129,.1); }

  .coach-msg { flex: 1; }
  .coach-msg p { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--txt2); margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .coach-msg p strong { color: var(--txt); }

  .coach-tag {
    font-size: 10px; font-family: var(--mono); padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 100px; font-weight: 600;
  }
  .bad-tag  { background: rgba(239,68,68,.1); color: #ef4444; }
  .good-tag { background: rgba(16,185,129,.1); color: #10b981; }

  .coach-col-note {
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--txt3); line-height: 1.5;
    font-style: italic; padding: 0 4px;
  }

  .coach-divider {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; gap: 12px; padding-top: 48px;
  }
  .coach-divider-line {
    width: 1px; height: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, var(--b2), transparent);
  }
  .coach-divider-vs {
    font-size: 11px; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--txt3);
    background: var(--bg3); border: 1px solid var(--b2);
    padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 6px; letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  /* ── 3 cartes étapes ── */
  .steps-wrap {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr auto 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }
  .step-card {
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--b);
    border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px;
    height: 100%; transition: border-color .2s, transform .2s;
  }
  .step-card:hover { border-color: var(--b2); transform: translateY(-3px); }
  .step-card-accent {
    border-color: rgba(59,130,246,.3);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--card), rgba(59,130,246,.04));
  }
  .step-card-accent:hover { border-color: var(--blue); }
  .step-card-top { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
  .step-badge {
    font-size: 10px; font-family: var(--mono); font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--blue2);
    background: rgba(59,130,246,.1); border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,.2);
    padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 100px;
  }
  .step-badge.active { background: var(--blue); color: #fff; border-color: var(--blue); }
  .step-icon { font-size: 22px; }
  .step-card-title {
    font-family: var(--disp); font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--txt); letter-spacing: -.2px; line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .step-card-title em { color: var(--blue2); font-style: normal; }
  .step-card-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--txt2); line-height: 1.65; flex: 1; }
  .step-card-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 5px; margin-top: 2px; }
  .step-tag-pill {
    font-size: 11px; font-family: var(--mono);
    padding: 2px 9px; border-radius: 100px; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .step-tag-pill.style { background: rgba(34,211,238,.08); color: var(--pulse); border: 1px solid rgba(34,211,238,.15); }
  .step-tag-pill.strat { background: rgba(59,130,246,.08); color: var(--blue2); border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,.15); }
  .step-tag-pill.session { background: rgba(16,185,129,.08); color: #10b981; border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,.15); }
  .step-trade-preview { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; margin-top: 2px; }
  .step-trade-row {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: var(--bg3); border: 1px solid var(--b);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 7px 10px; font-size: 11px;
  }
  .trade-pill { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .trade-pill.long  { background: rgba(16,185,129,.15); color: #10b981; }
  .trade-pill.short { background: rgba(239,68,68,.15); color: #ef4444; }
  .trade-asset { font-family: var(--mono); font-weight: 600; color: var(--txt); }
  .trade-meta  { color: var(--txt3); flex: 1; }
  .trade-pnl   { font-family: var(--mono); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .trade-pnl.pos { color: #10b981; }
  .trade-pnl.neg { color: #ef4444; }
  .step-insight-pill {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px;
    font-size: 11px; font-style: italic; color: var(--txt2);
    background: rgba(59,130,246,.06); border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,.15);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 12px; line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .insight-dot {
    width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--blue2); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--blue);
  }
  .step-arrow-h {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    color: var(--b2); padding: 0 12px; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .step-arrow-v { display: none; }

  /* ── Carrousel témoignages ── */
  .reviews-section { margin-bottom: 64px; }
  .reviews-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .reviews-stars-global {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    gap: 3px; margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .star { color: #f59e0b; font-size: 18px; }
  .reviews-score { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--txt); margin-left: 6px; }
  .reviews-count { font-size: 12px; color: var(--txt3); font-family: var(--mono); }
  .reviews-carousel { position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .reviews-track { display: flex; gap: 16px; transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.32,0.72,0,1); }
  .review-card {
    flex: 0 0 calc(33.333% - 11px);
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--b);
    border-radius: 14px; padding: 22px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px;
    transition: border-color .2s;
  }
  .review-card:hover { border-color: var(--b2); }
  .review-top { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .review-avatar {
    width: 38px; height: 38px; border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #000;
    font-family: var(--mono); flex-shrink: 0;
  }
